data.description: Adorable, single level, West facing home.  Inviting front porch, and oversized East facing patio are enjoyable in all seasons.  Home has hard wood floors, can lights, open concert living room/dining room, large picture front window, and fenced yard.  Enjoy BBQ's, a summer fire in your fire pit, Concord grapes, peaches  and mature landscape.   The charmer is ready to be yours!  Call for your private showing today!!
